{
  "chapter": 263,
  "chapter_summary": "第263章《生死边缘》摘要：\n\n项少龙被曹秋道刺成重伤，失血耗力倒在雪园。他包扎伤口后弃血浪宝剑、带百战宝刀，趁韩竭马车潜回临淄听松别馆。肖月潭为他治伤，二人分析局势：稷下学宫未传出失刀消息，曹秋道必已猜出是项少龙所为；韩闯出卖项少龙，凤菲与韩竭的秘密恋情得到证实。\n\n董淑贞前来探望，项少龙质问她与沙立暗通消息之事，她坚决否认。项少龙醒悟池子春是沙立内应，故意散布谣言离间。凤菲随后到来，项少龙发现她手上重现当年咸阳那只藏毒针的银指环——韩竭逼她来杀自己。项少龙以韩谒会见仲孙玄华之事反制凤菲，逼她暂时收手。他向凤菲讲述桃花源故事，令她崩溃痛哭。\n\n龙阳君闻讯赶来，项少龙将韩闯出卖之事和盘托出。龙阳君承诺查探韩闯是否已通知郭开，并愿助项少龙逃离临淄。项少龙婉拒，以免连累龙阳君。黄昏时分，解子元到访。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你的脸色为何这么难看？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "给曹秋道刺了一剑，脸色怎会好看。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "现在终于证实两件事，首先是凤菲的情郎确是韩竭，其次是韩闯出卖了我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "以你目前的状态，能到哪里去呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "有三天时间我当可复原，届时立即远走高飞，什么事都不去管。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "让我去告诉其他人说你病了。在此三天内你尽量不要离开听松别馆，这里总比外面安全。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "希望是这样吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "真奇怪，稷下学宫那边没有半点消息，好像昨晚没有发生过任何事情，但至少他们该传出百战宝刀失窃的事。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "你看曹秋道会否猜出昨晚偷刀的人是我项少龙呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "该是如此，只有惯用百战宝刀者方可把该刀的威力发挥得淋漓尽致，亦只有项少龙有本领把曹秋道杀得一时难以反击。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若曹秋道把你在此地的事告诉齐人，将使事情变得更复杂。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "横竖我都要走的，有什么大不了。最精彩是没有人敢明目张胆来对付我，韩闯便要假借他人之手来杀我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "李园他们有没有遣人来探听消息？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "照道理李园知道我曾找他，怎都该来看看我有什么事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "或者他是问心有愧，羞于面对你。唉！曹秋道真的那么厉害吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "他的剑术确达到突破体能限制、超凡入圣的境界，我对着他时完全一筹莫展，只有捱打的份儿。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你知否一般所谓高手与他对阵，连站都站不稳，不用动手就要掷剑认输。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "我也有那种感觉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "假设打从开始你用的是百战宝刀，胜负会是如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "结局肯定是连小命都不保。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你是真正的谦虚，且不把胜负放在心上。照我看你落在下风的最大原因，是因知道被好友出卖，心神震荡下无法燃起斗志，又一心想溜，所以发挥不出平时一半的实力。假若换了环境，用的是百战宝刀，你当是曹秋道的劲敌。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "现在我只想走得远远的，以后不再回来。以前无论在多么凶险恶劣的情况下，我从没有想过会死，但曹秋道那把剑却似能不住撩起我对死亡的恐惧。剑道达到这种境界，确是令人惊佩。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "凤菲来过没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "所有人都来过，就只她不闻不问，我对她早心淡了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好了点吗？唉！好好一个人，怎会忽然病倒呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "这事要问问老天爷才成。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "现在岂是哭泣的时候，二小姐为了自己的命运，必须坚强起来。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我的命运，只能由你们男人来决定，现在你病得不明不白，教人家怎办？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "又不是只得我一人帮你，二小姐何用凄惶至此？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你这么说是什么意思？我和秀真现在把希望只寄托在你身上，再没有三心两意。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "若是如此，昨天为何仍要和沙立暗通消息？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是谁造的谣？若我或秀真仍有和沙立勾结，教我们不得好死。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我和秀真现在是全心全意信任你，你……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "你有没有法子通知龙阳君，教他来见我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我明白了，此事淑贞立即去办，不会教人知道的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "幸好只是有点热，有谈先生为你诊治，很快该可痊愈。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "多谢大小姐关心，歌舞排练的情况如何？还有五天就是齐王寿宴举行的时候了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "听你说话的口气，像个陌生人般，我们的关系为何会弄成这样子的？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "听到你好生生一个人忽然病倒，哪还有什么心情。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你的脸色为何变得这么难看？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "为何不答人家？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "为何凤菲竟会在这种情况下遇上你？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "为何大小姐会看上肯与嫪毐同流合污的人？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要瞎猜！人家根本不认识韩竭。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "还要骗我？大小姐想不想知道昨晚韩竭送你回来后，去了见什么人？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "啊",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "大小姐若仍否认，我们就不用谈下去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他去见谁呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "仲孙玄华。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "大小姐好好地去想吧！我累得要命，须睡他一觉。只有在梦中，我沈良才可寻找躲避这充满欺诈仇杀的人世的桃花源。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么是桃花源？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人家现在该怎么办才好？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "此事还有待观察，韩竭去见仲孙玄华，并不代表什么，大小姐可否给小人一点时间去查看查看。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他至少该告诉我会去见仲孙玄华啊！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "很多男人习惯不把要做的事情说给女人听的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若换过是别人，在这种情况下，绝不会为韩竭说好话。唉！沈良啊！你究竟是怎样的一个人？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "你还不明白吗？我只是个不折不扣的大傻瓜，明知大小姐骗我害我，仍不忍见你伤心落泪。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "我差点给韩闯害得没有命见君上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这话怎说？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "雪刚停了，待这两日天气好转，奴家立即送你离开临淄。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "此事万万不可，否则君上将难逃贵国罪责。我现在只想知道韩闯有没有将我的事告诉郭开。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这事可包在我身上，现在回想起来，韩闯确曾在言语上向我试探，这贼子说的是一套，做的又是一套，真教人鄙视。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "text": "我不会怪他，他这么做是迫于无奈，凭着大家的交情，应付他亦不困难，最怕是他通知郭开，那就危险多了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "奴家立即去查，只要我向韩闯诈作想害你，保证他什么都说出来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 263,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    }
